# --- Secrets (never commit) ---
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# --- Python ---
**/.venv/
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo

# --- Node / Vite ---
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/dist-ssr/
**/*.local
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/pnpm-debug.log*

# --- OS / Editor ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
__MACOSX/
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
.idea/

# --- Logs ---
**/logs/
**/*.log

# --- Claude Code runtime (keep harness defs, drop runtime cache) ---
.claude/settings.local.json

# --- Railway ---
.railway/

# --- _workspace dev notes ---
# Cycle 리포트·prompt·draft는 미커밋. 사용자 매뉴얼 + 4 도메인 시나리오만 추적.
_workspace/*
!_workspace/user_manual.md
!_workspace/manual_test_scenario_construction.md
!_workspace/manual_test_scenario_heavy_industry.md
!_workspace/manual_test_scenario_manufacturing.md
!_workspace/manual_test_scenario_semiconductor.md

# --- 미사용 NotoSansKR weights ---
# 런타임 PDF는 Regular 1개만 임베드(pdfGenerate.ts:KO_FONT_URL).
# 다른 weight는 디스크에 두면 빌드 시 dist 복사로 +50 MB 낭비.
frontend/public/fonts/static/NotoSansKR-Black.ttf
frontend/public/fonts/static/NotoSansKR-Bold.ttf
frontend/public/fonts/static/NotoSansKR-ExtraBold.ttf
frontend/public/fonts/static/NotoSansKR-ExtraLight.ttf
frontend/public/fonts/static/NotoSansKR-Light.ttf
frontend/public/fonts/static/NotoSansKR-Medium.ttf
frontend/public/fonts/static/NotoSansKR-SemiBold.ttf
frontend/public/fonts/static/NotoSansKR-Thin.ttf
frontend/public/fonts/NotoSansKR-VariableFont_wght.ttf
